  "contentHtml": "\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Claude D’Souza, TNN\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                                                                                Claude D’Souza, TNN\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/87654367/TNN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TNN</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Jun 4, 2026 at 05:01 AM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                            <li>\n                                                        \n                                                            \n                                                                Read by \n                                                            \n                                                            100 Professionals\n                                                        \n                                                    </li>\n                                                                                    </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p><a href=\"/tag/udaipur\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Udaipur</a>: A five-year-old girl from Rajsamand district has made a full recovery from <a href=\"/tag/guillain-barr%c3%a9+syndrome+%28gbs%29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Guillain-Barré Syndrome (GBS)</a>, a rare and potentially life-threatening neurological disorder, after nearly 90 days of intensive treatment at the children’s hospital of <a href=\"/tag/maharana+bhupal+hospital\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Maharana Bhupal Hospital</a>, affiliated with <a href=\"/tag/ravindranath+tagore+medical+college+%28rntmc%29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ravindranath Tagore Medical College (RNTMC)</a>, Udaipur.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>The child was admitted with severe weakness in both legs and was later diagnosed with GBS, a condition in which the body's immune system attacks the nerves, leading to muscle weakness and, in severe cases, breathing difficulties. As her condition deteriorated, she was shifted to the <a href=\"/tag/pediatric+intensive+care+unit+%28picu%29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Pediatric Intensive Care Unit (PICU)</a> and placed on prolonged <a href=\"/tag/ventilator+support\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ventilator support</a>.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p><a href=\"/tag/dr+rahul+jain\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Dr Rahul Jain</a>, Principal and Controller of RNT Medical College, said the successful recovery demonstrated the capabilities of the hospital’s advanced critical care facilities and the dedication of its medical staff. The patient was discharged on May 31.Doctors said the severity of the illness required a tracheostomy, which was performed by the ENT department to facilitate long-term respiratory support. The child underwent intensive treatment and regular physiotherapy for nearly 80 days in the PICU. She was also provided protein-rich nutrition, including eggs and milk, free of cost to aid muscle recovery.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p><a href=\"/tag/dr+vivek+arora\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Dr Vivek Arora</a>, Head of the Pediatrics Department, said timely diagnosis, availability of immunoglobulin therapy and sustained critical care played a crucial role in saving the child. He added that maintaining prolonged ventilator support while preventing complications was a major challenge.During treatment, the child received five doses of <a href=\"/tag/intravenous+immunoglobulin+%28ivig%29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">intravenous immunoglobulin (IVIG)</a>, a critical therapy for GBS. Each vial cost around Rs 40,000, taking the total cost of the medicine to nearly Rs 2 lakh. The entire treatment expenditure of Rs 5.31 lakh was covered under the <a href=\"/tag/mukhyamantri+ayushman+arogya+%28maa%29+yojana\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mukhyamantri Ayushman Arogya (MAA) Yojana</a>.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>Unit Head Dr Mohammad Asif said the child was admitted on February 4 with complete loss of strength in both legs and worsening respiratory function. Following prompt treatment, round-the-clock monitoring, physiotherapy and nutritional support, she recovered fully and has now been discharged.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Claude D’Souza, TNN</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Claude D’Souza, TNN</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/87654367/TNN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TNN</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Jun 4, 2026 at 05:01 AM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Jun 4, 2026 at 05:01 AM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">2 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                                            \n                                        <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n            <!-- <figure class=\"top-newsletter-subs__icon-nl\" role=\"presentation\" aria-label=\"Newsletter icon\">\n                <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-newsletter.svg\" alt=\"Newsletter icon\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\">\n            </figure> -->\n        \n            \n                \n                    <h2>All about ETHealthworld industry right on your smartphone! </h2>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"/app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download the ETHealthworld App</a> and get the Realtime updates and Save your favourite articles.</li>\n                    </ul>\n                                            <!-- <div class=\"app-store-container desktop-view\">\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"\" aria-label=\"Play Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-g-play.png\" alt=\"\" />\n                            </a>\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"App Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"htt